response.original_title: 1992 FIA Formula One World Championship Season Review
response.overview: A must for formula 1 fans, and Nigel Mansell fans, this DUKE official review video captures the excitement and the drama of the 1992 Formula one world championship season, a year in which the dominance of Williams and particularly Nigel Mansell won him a much overdue world title. The video is well structured featuring all of the races plus much action from qualifying. A must have!
response.tagline: Formula 1 Grand Prix Review 1992 - Well Done Nigel !
response.title: 1992 FIA Formula One World Championship Season Review
